author: go4bob
title: Same on the cover same inside
review:
Ok in the last basic set #2 i did a review and said there were conflicting inventories but this one is ok what you see on the cover is what you get.
i haven't used this set, as i just bought it for its age on ebay with other kits. so in its day it would have been a very good set. 
For the Fan that is just a collector then this is a classic one to own.
